nodes.text: This Weequay was an associate of the Rodian bounty hunter Greedo during the Clone Wars.

Around 21 BBY, the Pantoran Chairman, Baron Notluwiski Papanoida and his son Ion came to Jabba's Palace on Tatooine looking for Greedo, whom they suspected of kidnapping the chairman's daughters, Chi Eekway and Che Amanwe. Brainee and this Weequay were playing a game of chance cubes with Greedo, when they were informed by Trella Bare'Ah, Greedo's Twi'lek girlfriend, about Papanoida's inquiries.

Following Greedo, Brainee and this Weequay attempted to capture Papanoida and Ion, but the Baron turned the tables on them and in turn captured Greedo, holding him at Vibroblade-point, while this Weequay captured Ion. Papanoida brought the group before Jabba the Hutt and presented evidence which forced Greedo to confess to his part in the kidnapping.
